Package org.webcurator.domain

Interface Summary
AgencyOwnable The interface implemented by objects that are owned by an agency.
AnnotationDAO The interface that defines the Data Access Object for loading and saving annotations.
BaseDAO Base DAO interface.
HarvestCoordinatorDAO The interface for accessing data from the persistent store used by the HarvestCoordinator.
InTrayDAO Persistence methods commonly used by the In-tray
PermissionTemplateDAO Persistance Interface for the managing the Permission Template Request object
ProfileDAO DAO for loading/saving Profiles to the database.
RejReasonDAO The Rejection Reason DAO provides access to rejection reason data from the persistent data store.
SchedulePatternFactory An interface for the Schedule Pattern Factory.
SiteDAO The interface used for accessing persistent Harvest Authorisation data.
TargetDAO The TargetDAO provides access to targets, target groups and their related objects from the persistent store.
TargetInstanceDAO The object for accessing TargetInstances from the persistent store.
UserOwnable The interface implemented by objects that are owned by a user.
UserRoleDAO The User Role DAO provides access to User, Role and Agency data from the persistent data store.
